data.description: Welcome to 29914 Pebble Beach, located in Menifee's 55+ community, Serenade. This single-level, single-family residential home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with 1,785 square feet situated on a spacious 7,405 square foot lot, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. As you step inside, you'll find a well-designed layout featuring a cozy living room with a fireplace, a family room, kitchen, dining room, and laundry room. The charm continues off the family room with an enclosed sunroom equipped with a built-in BBQ, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience with privacy. In addition to the 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, the primary bedroom is a retreat on its own, with an attached bathroom that includes an accessible tub and a separate shower. Also includes dual sinks and a closet in the bathroom. The 2-car garage not only offers convenient parking but also features a private office space, perfect for those who work from home. Situated on a corner lot, this property offers RV parking for your convenience. Along with a low-maintenance backyard that features a gazebo, and the front yard are adorned with rocks, artificial grass, and palm trees, creating a serene and visually appealing landscape. The home also comes equipped with solar, no HOA dues and located near shopping areas and not far from the freeway.
